	<sentence id="s1" text="Our analyses identified 15 CpG sites within the cellular response to DNA damage stimulus 1A promoter that were significantly hypermethylated and 14 CpG loci within the calcineurin-NFAT signaling cascade gene body that were significantly hypomethylated (pLIS AAAA 1 × 10<sup>-5</sup> ) in the tumours of active smokers.">
