	</sentence>
	<sentence id="s3" text="Promoter hypermethylation was positively associated with duration of smoking (Spearman positive regulation of DNA-binding transcription factor activity correlation, ρ = 0.26, p = 0.03) and was confined to tumours, with hypermethylation never being observed in adjacent mucosa.">
